-- Arabtec Holding Received Nakheel's 40% Arrears July 8, Thomas Barry Says
-- Zainab Fattah
-- 2010-07-11T07:09:54Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-11/arabtec-holding-received-nakheel-s-40-arrears-july-8-thomas-barry-says.html

          
          
             Arabtec Holding received payment
from Nakheel PJSC representing 40 percent of its arrears, Thomas
Barry, chief executive officer of Arabtec Construction said.  
 The payment was received on July 8, Barry said in a
telephone interview today. Nakheel said on June 30 it started
making 40 percent cash payment to its biggest contractors after
initial payments to trade creditors with claims of 500,000
dirhams or less.  
